Oh, one thing that might not be obvious looking at this without color (I color coded it in excel which makes certain things easier to see), is that there is only a general relationship between lifespan and working life. Obviously, to have the longest Prime and Working Life, you need the lifespan to support it, and a purebred Wracky has the longest of all three.
